- "Minimum flight duration" is the shortest flight duration for each aircraft;
- "Maximum flight duration" is the longest flight duration for each aircraft;
- "Aircraft type" refers to the category or model of the aircraft.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT flight_id) 
FROM flight_locations
WHERE g_lat > 3743128.0 AND g_long < -12205687.0;

